      <title>监管机构称爱尔兰预算计划可能给经济增添压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/irish-budget-plans-could-add-pressure-to-economy-watchdog-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱尔兰财政监管机构警告称，爱尔兰政府在即将于十月公布的预算中违反了自己的支出规定，这给经济增加了“不必要的”压力，而且有可能在日后不得不违背承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/irish-budget-plans-could-add-pressure-to-economy-watchdog-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 05:54:01 GMT</pubDate>
